  - Life-Love=Prayer-Meditation-Contemplation=Man Created for Contemplation
By: Angelus Silesius
---
Demons blaspheme God, beasts ignore Him, men love Him, while angels
contemplate His light without removing their gaze. By this even canst
thou know whom to call angel, man, beast, or demon.
